## 3. System Prompt Assembler Class

- [ ] 3.1 Create `SystemPromptAssembler` class in `src/bun/engine/execution/system-prompt-assembler.ts`
- [ ] 3.2 Implement `SystemPromptPart` interface (`content`, `order`, `source`):
  - `order` is numeric (lower = earlier/higher weight)
  - `source` is `"custom" | "workflow" | "stage"`
  - `addPart(content, order, source)` — adds ordered part
- [ ] 3.3 Implement `fromConfig(config, boardId, columnId)` — loads workflow+stage instructions from config as parts
