- [ ] 3.4 Implement `addCustomPrompts(customPrompts)` — adds custom prompt content as parts with orders 0–99 sorted by parsed priority
- [ ] 3.5 Implement `assemble()` — joins all parts by order, returns joined string or `undefined`
